---
Apply a label to a message

Usage: mxr label [OPTIONS] <NAME> [MESSAGE_ID]

Arguments:
  <NAME>        Label name
  [MESSAGE_ID]  Message ID

Options:
      --search <SEARCH>  
      --yes              
      --dry-run          
  -h, --help             Print help
